n twice (both necessary)\n\n### 10-1-agentdriver-interface-types — verification (2026-04-03T06:35)\n\n- 51 pre-existing lint warnings (unused vars) — unrelated to this story\n- `codeharness verify` warns about missing Showboat and exec-plan — non-blocking\n- ALL_PASS 11/11 ACs with real evidence\n\n## Token Report — verification\n- Total tool calls: 15\n- By tool: Bash: 10, Read: 5, Write: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npm run test:coverage` (~50 lines), `npm run test:unit` (~40 lines)\n- Files read: 5 unique, 5 total reads\n- Redundant operations: `npm run build` ran twice (minor)\n\n### 10-3-claude-code-driver-extraction — create-story (2026-04-03T06:58)\n\n- **No `agent-dispatch.ts` at `src/lib/agents/`** — lives at `src/lib/agent-dispatch.ts` (one directory up). Story correctly references actual path.\n- **Epic 10 status is `backlog` despite 2 done stories** — inconsistent, not modified per instructions.\n- **Plugin pass-through uncertainty** — Agent SDK `query()` plugin support not fully documented. AC #6 may need adjustment.\n\n## Token Report — create-story\n- Total tool calls: 18\n- By tool: Bash: 2, Read: 10, Glob: 5, Grep: 4, Write: 1\n- Files read: 13 unique, 13 total reads\n- Redundant operations: none\n\n### 10-3-claude-code-driver-extraction — dev-story (2026-04-03T07:02)\n\n- **ResultEvent error fields workaround:** `ResultEvent` type lacks `error`/`errorCategory` fields. Driver uses type intersection — mild type system workaround.\n- **DispatchOpts lacks systemPrompt:** Interface doesn't include `systemPrompt`. Consistent with 10-1 design.\n- **Plugin SDK support uncertain:** Passes `plugins` directly to SDK options — silently ignored if unsupported.\n\n## Token Report — dev-story\n- Total tool calls: 16\n- By tool: Bash: 5, Read: 8, Edit: 3, Write: 2, Glob: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npm run test:unit` (~500 lines), `npx tsc --noEmit` (~27 lines), `npm run build` (~20 lines)\n- Files read: 9 unique, 9 total reads\n- Redundant operations: none\n","str