n1035\t\n1036\t### Recurring issues (tracked across sessions)\n1037\t\n1038\t| Issue | Sessions Seen | Escalation |\n1039\t|-------|---------------|------------|\n1040\t| Proof format mismatch (h2 vs h3, verdict format) | 4 sessions | MEDIUM — still not fixed in verification subagent prompt |\n1041\t| `config.yaml` path mismatch | 3 sessions | LOW — never blocks, just noise |\n1042\t| Redundant vitest coverage runs | 5+ sessions | MEDIUM — escalated last session |\n1043\t\n1044\t---\n1045\t\n1046\t## 3. Cost Analysis\n1047\t\n1048\t### Parent-level cost (from cost-report.md)\n1049\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01RQCtb27pZs291zmdmd8MaZ","session_id":"ccf790f5-4b27-4b46-b089-256c4e0022f0","uuid":"77ddc684-3a89-42b6-8630-bf92f5479b1c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T07:15:22.320Z"}
