{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RQCtb27pZs291zmdmd8MaZ","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrospective written to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-04-03.md`, appended after the Session 11 retro with a `---` separator.\n\n**Summary of findings:**\n\n- **Story 10-3-claude-code-driver-extraction:** All 4 phases (create, dev, review, verify) passed first try. 10/10 ACs. 72 total tool calls across subagents.\n- **Code review caught 2 HIGH bugs:** `ResultEvent` type was missing `error`/`errorCategory` fields (unsafe casts), and test assertions used double-casts masking type mismatches. Both fixed.\n- **Cost:** ~$4.00 estimated. Code-review was the most expensive phase (22 tool calls, 9 edits). Dev phase produced ~500 lines of test output — flagged as reducible.\n- **Recurring issues:** `codeharness stats` still broken (7th session), AGENTS.md staleness growing, epic status not auto-updating. Proof format issue did NOT recur — possible improvement.\n- **25 action items tracked** (8 carried forward, 5 new this session)."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a48125e364748b181 (use SendMessage with to: 'a48125e364748b181' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 34333\ntool_uses: 11\nduration_ms: 114786</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ccf790f5-4b27-4b46-b089-256c4e0022f0","uuid":"8bae60fe-f448-4165-a305-3ca3a133486e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T07:17:02.676Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Run /retrospective for the current sprint session.\n\nSprint status: _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/sprint-status.yaml\nSession issues log: _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md\nCost report: Run `codeharness stats --json` to get token consumption data.\n\nCRITICAL: Read the session issues log FIRST. This file contains real problems, workarounds, bugs, and observations reported by every subagent that